<div id="landing-container">
  <div class="diagonal__header" style="background-image: url(/assets/features/landing_image.jpg);">
    <div class="diagonal__header--lead">WORK HARD LIVE LATER</div>
    <h3 class="diagonal__header--body">Use visual analytics to track how your daily limit fluctuates</h3>
    <a href="/users/sign_up"><button id="sign_up">Learn with BrunchBucks</button></a>
  </div>
  <div id="diagonal-container">
    <div id="diagonal">
      <div class="diagonal__adhead">
        <h2>Three Simple Steps</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="diagonal__adbox">
        <div class="diagonal__adbox--l">
          <h4>Calculate daily spending limits</h4>
          <p>Update us after expenses and we'll do the rest of the math for you. We keep track of your past spending quotas, days left in the month, and what your last recorded spending was.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="diagonal__adbox--r">
          <%= image_tag "features/dsq_calculator_panel.png", class: "shadow" %>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="diagonal__adbox">
        <div class="diagonal__adbox--l">
          <%= image_tag "features/dsq_chart_panel.png", class: "shadow" %>
        </div>
        <div class="diagonal__adbox--r">
          <h4>Visualize your spending habits</h4>
          <p>We'll calculate and track your progress on your spending history. Get instant feedback on how much you can spend per day and how it flucutates throughout the month. Identify key patterns that reflect your spending habits through out the month.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="diagonal__adbox">
        <div class="diagonal__adbox--l">
          <h4>Put your money to work</h4>
          <p>Check out our blog on money hacks to tweak and customize your budget to what works best for you. Learn about financial milestones and grow your money where it's supposed to be. Identify places to improve your budget based on visualized spending habits.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="diagonal__adbox--r">
          <%= image_tag "features/blog_panel.png", class: "shadow" %>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="diagonal__footer">
    <div class="diagonal__footer--lead">
      Join us on BrunchBucks
    </div>
    <div class="diagonal__footer--body">
      <p>One last thing we want to mention is that budgeting isn't supposed to feel constricting. We've found it to be a liberating feeling. A solid budgeting plan helps you to know when to splurge money or tighten up the wallet. Let us give you the freedom of guilt free spending.</p>
      <a href="/users/sign_up" class="cbtn cbtn-4"><span>GET STARTED WITH US</span></a>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
